results.query:
Select A.ID, B.Text, B.Lemma,
Case when A.M = 1 then 'M' when A.A = 1 then 'A' when A.C = 1 then 'C' when A.T = 1 then 'T' else '' end as TMatch,
Case when A.M1 = 1 then 'M1' when A.A1 = 1 then 'A1' when A.C1 = 1 then 'C1' when A.T1 = 1 then 'T1' else '' end as LMatch,
B.POS, B.Book, B.Chapter, B.Verse,
A.M, A.A, A.C, A.T, A.M1, A.A1, A.C1, A.T1
from MattColors A left join (Select Id, Text, Lemma, POS, Book, Chapter, Verse from Gospels where Book = 'Matt' and Chapter = 9 and Verse between 1 and 8) B on A.ID = B.ID left join (Select Id, MattRef, MarkRef, LukeRef from Alignment) C where B.ID = C.ID

column.name: CASE WHEN A.M = 1 THEN 'M' WHEN A.A = 1 THEN 'A' WHEN A.C = 1 THEN 'C' WHEN A.T = 1 THEN 'T' ELSE '' END
CASE WHEN A.M1 = 1 THEN 'M1' WHEN A.A1 = 1 THEN 'A1' WHEN A.C1 = 1 THEN 'C1' WHEN A.T1 = 1 THEN 'T1' ELSE '' END
